* Carnage sprang to her feet and snarled at the other raptor, now it knew 
that she didn't take being surprised lightly!!
She took a step back then snapped in the other raptor's direction, she 
flexed her inner toe claws then rammed them into the ground and brought them 
back up.
Carnage roared, took a step forward and snapped at the raptor again. She 
hatted surprises, especially when they were rude and annoying!
Carnage was furious, was this attacker going to attack properly or was it 
just one big bluff?!
She snarled and snapped again, her mech fluid surging with the need to rip 
this attacker apart!*

" Coward!!! Face me!!!"
